                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; the word sälam; the owner’s name; several lines or groups of lines on the incipit page of the commemorative notices for each month; one or two initial lines of each commemorative notice; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of the Ethiopian numbers.</rubric>
